platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.ta.k: Get a reservation in a few taps

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Got a date to impress? Maybe you’re trying to celebrate your anniversary or meet up with a group of friends to grab something to eat. OpenTable makes it unbelievably easy to find the perfect place for the right occasion. Now save yourself some trouble by searching, exploring, and making a reservation all in one app.
無論是約會、特別紀念日，或與朋友聚餐，你都能輕鬆找到適合的餐廳。搜尋、瀏覽、預訂三個步驟，一款 App 就能辦妥。

It’s unbelievably easy to find the perfect place for the right occasion, whether it’s a date, a special anniversary or a quick bite with friends. Search, explore and make a reservation, all in one app.
デートや特別な記念日、友だちとの軽い食事など、目的にふさわしいレストランが驚くほど簡単に見つかります。検索から、詳細の確認、予約まで、一つのアプリですべてが完結します。

Got a date to impress? Maybe you’re trying to celebrate your anniversary, or simply meet up with a group of friends and grab something to eat. OpenTable will make it unbelievably easy for you to find the perfect place for the right occasion. Now save yourself some trouble by searching, exploring, and making a reservation all in one app.
有了這款 App，你便能輕鬆為約會、紀念日或與朋友聚餐找到最合適的餐廳，從搜尋、挑選到預訂一次搞定。

Trouvez l’endroit idéal pour la bonne occasion en toute simplicité, que ce soit pour un dîner aux chandelles, un anniversaire ou un repas avec vos proches. Recherchez, parcourez et réservez depuis l’app.

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.sh.k: A guid to the most famous restaurants around you.
Dénichez et réservez une bonne table à tous les coups.
